        <h2>Platform</h2>
        <p>
          The Platform is a complete ruggedized, full-sized multitouch table that comes with a powerful integrated PC with an i7 quad core, built-in RFID, and support for up to 60 touch points. It is available in either 46&quot; or 55&quot; variations with a standard HD or 4K Ultra HD display.
        </p>
        <a class="platform" href="platform">View Selections</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="product-category" id-autoplay>
    <video poster="{{theme.link}}/images/products/Drafting.png">
